| High Section 1 | Lawyer Calculus (A+B+C) | Your agent is optimizing for their own career/efficiency over your outcome. |
| High Section 2 | Judicial Calculus (E+R) | The judge is optimizing for docket speed or avoiding the work of a complex ruling. |
| High Both | Systemic Collusion | You are trapped in a "closed-loop" where the professionals are working together to close the file. |
üõ† The Patches: Immediate Strategic Responses
